<body class="about-page">


  <main class="container">
    <h1>About CardVerse</h1>
    <p>
      CardVerse is a free, fan-made Pokémon TCG tool that lets you explore, search, and tag cards using unique descriptors like 
      <em>cute</em>, <em>flying</em>, <em>spooky</em>, and more. Our goal is to build the most fun, community-driven Pokédex for Pokémon cards.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>What You Can Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>🔍 Search cards using community-submitted tags</li>
        <li>🏷️ Submit your own tags for cards</li>
        <li>📁 Create and share collections — public or private</li>
        <li>✨ Discover new cards through visual and tag-based browsing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Join the Community</h2>
      <p>
        💬 <a href="https://discord.gg/h8ha9489tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Join our Discord</a> to chat, submit feedback, or hang out with other collectors!
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🐛 Report Bugs</h2>
        <p>
            Found a bug or something not working as expected? We’d love to know!
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>🧰 Use the <strong>“Report a Bug”</strong> button at the bottom of the homepage</li>
            <li>💬 Or share details in our <strong>#bug-reports</strong> channel on <a href="https://discord.gg/h8ha9489tr" target="_blank">Discord</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Helpful bug reports include screenshots, card IDs, browser/device info, and steps to reproduce.
        </p>
    </section>


    <section>
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <dl>
        <dt>Do I need an account?</dt>
        <dd>Nope! You can search and browse without logging in. Signing up is only needed to save collections or tag cards.</dd>

        <dt>Can I submit tags?</dt>
        <dd>Yes! Use the tag form on any card detail page. All tags are reviewed by moderators before appearing publicly.</dd>

        <dt>Is this official?</dt>
        <dd>No — this is a fan-made project and is not affiliated with Pokémon or The Pokémon Company in any way.</dd>

        <dt>Why don’t some cards have tags?</dt>
        <dd>The community is helping build the database! The more people tag, the better the tool becomes.</dd>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🛠 Roadmap</h2>
      <p>This section is updated regularly with new features in development.</p>
      <dl><dt>Public Testers Needed!</dt>
      <dd>Please contact <a href="mailto:support@mycardverse.com">support@mycardverse.com</a> if interested.</dd></dl>

      <h3>Currently Working On</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>📱 Swipe optimization for mobile tagging</li>
        <li>🔗 Social sharing buttons for collections</li>
        <li>🧠 Advanced Searching in the /search page</li>
        <li>🎯 Tag Optimization in /tagging-center</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Planned Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>🤖 AI-powered tag suggestions</li>
        <li>💰 Collection value tracking</li>
        <li>👤 Improved public profiles</li>
        <li>🎴 Pack builder by tag themes</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>📬 Contact Support</h2>
        <p>
            If you have questions, need help, or just want to get in touch, feel free to reach out.
        </p>
        <p>
            📧 Email us anytime at <a href="mailto:support@mycardverse.com">support@mycardverse.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            We’re happy to help with account issues, feature requests, or general questions about the tool.
        </p>
    </section>


